      "name": "DragonForce",
      "description": "DragonForce is a ransomware-as-a-service (RaaS) group active since 2023, known for exploiting SimpleHelp RMM vulnerabilities, exfiltrating data with Restic, and encrypting victim systems. The group uses double extortion and operates public-facing blogs and data leak sites.",
